            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國4月連續第11個月維持貸款市場報價利率不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/64M9sATm19uqdzdtp4hFYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7B05U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 中國4月連續第11個月維持基準貸款利率不變,符合市場預期,顯示在經濟狀況改善的背景下,政策傾向保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國人民銀行週一公佈的數據顯示,一年期貸款市場報價利率(LPR)維持在3.00%,而作為房貸參考的五年期LPR則維持在3.50%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一決定出爐之際,近期數據顯示全球第二大經濟體展現韌性,第一季度經濟增長加速至約5%,降低了大規模貨幣寬鬆的迫切性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師表示,隨著通脹顯現企穩跡象且外部風險持續存在,央行可能更傾向依賴定向政策工具,如流動性注入或存款準備金率調整,而非全面降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B4%E6%9C%88%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E7%AC%AC11%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%A0%B1%E5%83%B9%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-022553851.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 10:47:07",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜據報Meta擬下月全球裁員一成涉近8,000人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜據報Meta擬下月全球裁員一成涉近8,000人\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜據報<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Meta\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Meta\">Meta</a>擬下月全球裁員一成涉近8,000人</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透》引述消息報道，Meta(美：META)計劃下月20日展開今年首波大規模裁員，後續還將有更多裁員行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息指，首輪裁員將裁減全球約10%員工，即近8,000人。公司並計劃下半年進一步裁員，但日期和規模等具體細節未定，高層或會按人工智能技術的發展情況調整計劃。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">早前有報道指Meta計劃裁減全球兩成或以上員工。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1meta%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1-%E6%88%90%E6%B6%89%E8%BF%918-000%E4%BA%BA-021029249.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 10:17:09",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "匯鑽科AI矽光子接單加速且水冷散熱組件自主生產 泰國新增產能將動工",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oxphmokgHLchgvnc9.l1KA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/448eecef96539ded3f0fde419e1a0c89\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%AF%E9%91%BD%E7%A7%91ai%E7%9F%BD%E5%85%89%E5%AD%90%E6%8E%A5%E5%96%AE%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%94%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%B7%E6%95%A3%E7%86%B1%E7%B5%84%E4%BB%B6%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E7%94%A2%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%87%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%A5-022714649.html",
