            "title": "美國扣押伊朗船隻後油價飆漲7%,荷莫茲海峽再度關閉",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國表示已扣押一艘伊朗貨船,而<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"德黑蘭\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:德黑蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/德黑蘭\">德黑蘭</a>在週末短暫開放荷莫茲海峽後再度關閉該航道,油價週一亞洲早盤交易時段大幅上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">布蘭特原油期貨一度飆漲7%至每桶97.50美元,截至美國東部時間18:56(北京時間22:56)報每桶95.71美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普表示,軍方向一艘試圖突破美國封鎖的伊朗籍貨船開火,並扣押了該船隻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據國營媒體報導,伊朗譴責此舉並誓言報復。此前德黑蘭在週末重新開放荷莫茲海峽,但不到24小時就再度關閉。伊朗最初宣布重新開放後,油價週五曾暴跌超過9%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-592112ab-6a3b-3057-9b3d-6019279ba58b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德黑蘭隨後在週末向數艘試圖穿越該航道的船隻開火。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些事態發展顯示美國與伊朗之間的緊張局勢惡化,並引發外界質疑在4月21日兩週停火協議結束前,是否還有可能進行更多和平談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,美國特使將於週一晚間抵達伊斯蘭堡進行更多談判,而伊朗國營媒體則報導稱德黑蘭已拒絕進一步的和平談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國與以色列對伊朗的戰爭已進入連續第八週,週末的事態發展顯示局勢幾乎沒有立即降溫的空間。荷莫茲海峽石油運輸持續受阻,預計將在未來數日繼續支撐原油價格。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該航道供應全球約五分之一的石油消費量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">戰爭爆發後,油價曾飆升至每桶近120美元,但在川普大力宣傳與德黑蘭進行和平談判後,過去兩週回吐了大部分漲幅。但上週末舉行的談判進展甚微,華盛頓和德黑蘭是否會再次會面進行對話目前仍不明朗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
